# MAUI XAML Pattern Rules

## CommandParameter 타입 명시 ⚠️ (필수!)

### ❌ 잘못된 패턴
```xml
<Button CommandParameter="1.0" />      <!-- String -->
<Button CommandParameter="123" />      <!-- String -->
<Button CommandParameter="true" />     <!-- String -->
```

### ✅ 올바른 패턴
```xml
<Button Command="{Binding ChangeRadiusCommand}">
    <Button.CommandParameter>
        <x:Double>1.0</x:Double>
    </Button.CommandParameter>
</Button>

<Button.CommandParameter>
    <x:Int32>123</x:Int32>
</Button.CommandParameter>

<Button.CommandParameter>
    <x:Boolean>True</x:Boolean>
</Button.CommandParameter>
```

## 타입 변환 테이블

| C# 타입 | XAML 표현 |
|---------|-----------|
| `double` | `<x:Double>3.14</x:Double>` |
| `int` | `<x:Int32>42</x:Int32>` |
| `bool` | `<x:Boolean>True</x:Boolean>` |
| `string` | `"Hello"` (따옴표) |

## Binding 패턴

```xml
<!-- Property Binding -->
<Label Text="{Binding UserName}" />

<!-- Command Binding -->
<Button Command="{Binding SaveCommand}" />

<!-- TwoWay Binding -->
<Entry Text="{Binding SearchText, Mode=TwoWay}" />

<!-- Converter -->
<Label IsVisible="{Binding IsLoading, Converter={StaticResource InvertedBoolConverter}}" />
```

## StaticResource 사용

```xml
<!-- 색상 -->
<Label TextColor="{StaticResource PrimaryCTA}" />

<!-- 스타일 -->
<Label Style="{StaticResource Heading1}" />

<!-- Converter -->
<Label IsVisible="{Binding Phone, Converter={StaticResource IsNotNullConverter}}" />
```

## Grid Layout

```xml
<Grid ColumnDefinitions="3*,7*" RowDefinitions="Auto,*">
    <!-- Column 0, Row 0 -->
    <Label Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="0" Text="Left" />
    
    <!-- Column 1, Row 0 -->
    <Label Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="0" Text="Right" />
</Grid>
```

